<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>登录超时</title>
    <style>
        BODY
        {
            color: #000000;
            background-color: white;
            font-family: Verdana;
            margin-left: 0px;
            margin-top: 0px;
        }

        A
        {
            color: green;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .heading1
        {
            background-color: #F9F1E9;
            line-height: 22px;
            border: #E5BD93 1px solid;
            color: #000;
            font-family: Tahoma;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .msg
        {
            background: url('/theme/images/sorry.jpg') no-repeat;
            padding: 20px 0px 30px 120px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-left: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/Theme/scripts/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/Theme/Plugins/Dialog/Dialog.yui.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/Theme/scripts/UI.yui.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/Theme/scripts/DAO.yui.js"></script>
<body>
    <script>
        var currentUrlPath = '@HttpContext.Current.Request.Url.AbsolutePath';
        function login() { if (window.location != window.top.location) { DAO.LoginBox(currentUrlPath); } else window.top.location.href = '/Account/Login' }; login();
        function refresh() { window.location.href = currentUrlPath; }
    </script>
    <div class="msg">
        <p class="heading1">
            登录超时，请重新登录!，登录成功后，刷新该页面!如登录框未弹出
                [<a href='javascript:;' onclick='login()'>请点此登录</a>] 
                [<a href='javascript:;' onclick='refresh()'>刷新该页 </a>]
        </p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
